      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><style>[data-colorid=vbayzd2791]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=vbayzd2791]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ijmqw4z8s8]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ijmqw4z8s8]{color:#004eb3}</style><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_logo.svg\" width=\"102\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/405700767/RenderManUniversity_logo.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1743656646136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=59&amp;height=73\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/405700767/RenderManUniversity_logo.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1743656646136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"73\" data-width=\"59\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"405962823\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_logo.svg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/svg+xml\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"405700767\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"df486496-e966-4d07-b038-b703bfca376e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/405700767/RenderManUniversity_logo.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1743656646136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=59&amp;height=73 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/405700767/RenderManUniversity_logo.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1743656646136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=59&amp;height=73 1x\" /></span><hr /><iframe align=\"middle\" allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"a429b6de-6102-41ed-8a08-efc39d3c7b8a\" data-macro-id=\"d16558a074733b92c3f39c3bc7e465192a7f60a97cba2889d8e54f7212a93a44\" data-macro-name=\"iframe\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"500\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-modals allow-orientation-lock allow-pointer-lock allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-presentation allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"auto\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/1039129158?h=d9fe405f6b&amp;title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0\" width=\"100%\">\n    \n</iframe>\n<h1 id=\"CharacterShadingResources-Workingonacharacter?\"><span data-colorid=\"ijmqw4z8s8\">Working on a character?</span></h1><p>RenderMan has a load of great character shading resources; luckily for you, we&rsquo;ve gathered them all here for you in one place.</p><hr /><h3 id=\"CharacterShadingResources-SkinShading\"><span data-colorid=\"vbayzd2791\">Skin Shading</span></h3><p>Rassoul Edji created this very cool Samurai character.  Here you can read how he achieved such a high-quality character.  You can also download the model and inspect the shaders, learning from him and increasing the realism of your characters</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"samurai_studioHDRIs.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/405700767/samurai_studioHDRIs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1743657097722&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/405700767/samurai_studioHDRIs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1743657097722&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"405733440\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"samurai_studioHDRIs.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"405700767\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d95e127c-1e53-4d89-a159-ef6501ef72a3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/405700767/samurai_studioHDRIs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1743657097722&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/405700767/samurai_studioHDRIs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1743657097722&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><p /><p />"
